peerlists:
	a list of peers that every user has.
	peer request : like friend request but with peers


to asign a task to someone:
	they should be on you peer list
	you need to send them a request first, which they need to approve


notifications:
	every time you recieve a peer request
	every time someone has accepted your peer request
	every time you recieve a task request
	every time someone has accepted your task request
	every time some task you are involved in has some development(someone gets assigned a task/a task has had some changes)

	